## Prerequisites

- Rust {{rustEdition}} or higher
- Cargo

## Getting Started

### Build
```bash
cargo build
```

### Run
```bash
cargo run
```

### Test
```bash
cargo test
```

### Format
```bash
cargo fmt
```

### Lint
```bash
cargo clippy
```

## API Endpoints

- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /api/v1/hello` - Example endpoint
{{#if enableMetrics}}
- `GET /metrics` - Prometheus metrics
{{/if}}

## Configuration

Environment variables:
- `RUST_LOG` - Log level (default: info)
- `PORT` - Server port (default: 8080)

## Docker

Build image:
```bash
docker build -t {{projectName}} .
```

Run container:
```bash
docker run -p 8080:8080 {{projectName}}
```

